      "content": "that's a good start, but it feels a bit generic. can you make it more specific? i want it to really call out the \"radicalism\" i mentioned. focus on how their policies—like the way they view gender or parenting—are actually attacks on the family. make the contrast between our candidate and their agenda feel like a fight for the soul of the country. make it sound like there's no middle ground.",
